Hi, by 'excavation' do you want to actually remove the blocks from the mesh, or you are okay with changing the blocks property to be really weak (lower the youngs_modulus or something like that)
if so, you can have the state map/flag material for each element (via PropertyReadFile), and modify the material property of each element (for example youngs_modulus) based on the state
PropertyReadFile can read .csv file and give the value for each element (1 to n_th element == 1 to n_th row of the file)
